I have some recommendations for Mage candidates that could be good APCs for Bottom Lane:
 {{champion:136}} {{champion:268}} {{champion:69}} {{champion:30}} {{champion:127}} {{champion:90}} {{champion:13}} {{champion:50}} {{champion:163}} {{champion:4}} {{champion:45}} 

Of course, all these can't just be able to be in Bottom Lane. I was just naming some of the Mages with good potential for Bottom Lane success considering their play styles. The main ones to me that could be good candidates for this line of work are Azir, Cassiopeia, Karthus, Twisted Fate, and Veigar in particular.
